dcterms:description: Spider is a large-scale human-labeled dataset for complex and cross-domain semantic parsing and text-to-SQL tasks, consisting of pairs of natural language questions and corresponding SQL translations, organized into four difficulty levels.
dcterms:title: Spider

dcterms:description: Termite is a new, unseen dataset created for evaluating the text-to-SQL task, designed to be a fresh resource that is not publicly available or easily retrievable, thus minimizing the risk of data contamination.
dcterms:title: Termite
